that during the operation,

907
01:35:53,550 --> 01:35:57,714
the load tends to force
its way towards the rear doors

908
01:35:57,854 --> 01:36:03,156
and ends up Iying in this area.

909
01:36:03,293 --> 01:36:07,320
Consequently, the front axle
is not overloaded.

910
01:36:07,831 --> 01:36:09,162
Three:

911
01:36:09,299 --> 01:36:13,292
